Algorithm ACO(Graph G, Number_of_Ants m, Iterations I)

1. Initialize pheromone value τ on all edges
2. Place m ants randomly on graph nodes

3. Repeat for I iterations
      For each ant k
            Construct a path by choosing next node
            based on probability rule

      Evaluate path cost for each ant

      Update pheromone trails:
            Evaporate pheromone on all edges
            Add pheromone to edges belonging to best paths

4. Store best path found

5. Return best path
